//fldigi macro definition file extended
// Custom macro set for UT3UDX
// Valid Fldigi format (UTF-8, no BOM)
// 4x12 button layout for Fldigi macro panel
// Updated and structured by ChatGPT (2025-10-05)
// All macros unified under BPSK31 mode
// Organized according to standard QSO flow

// =======================================================
// Button Row 1 — CQ / Answering
// =======================================================

/$ 0 1.1 Calling CQ
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<IDLE:0.25>
CQ CQ CQ de <MYCALL> <MYCALL>
CQ CQ CQ de <MYCALL> <MYCALL> pse k
<RX>

 
/$ 1 1.2 QRZ?
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<IDLE:0.25>
QRZ? QRZ? de <MYCALL> <MYCALL> kn
<IDLE:0.25>
<RX>

 
/$ 2 1.3 Calling CQ (Alt)
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<IDLE:0.25>
CQ CQ CQ de <MYCALL> <MYCALL>
CQ CQ CQ de <MYCALL> <MYCALL> pse k
<RX>

 
/$ 3 2.1 Answer A CQ Call
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<RXRSID:off>
<CALL> de <MYCALL> name is <MYNAME> <MYRST> <INFO1> btu <CALL> de <MYCALL> kn
<RX>

 
/$ 4 2.2 Answer A CQ
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<RXRSID:off>
*** <CALL> <CALL> *** de <MYCALL>
Hello, my name is <MYNAME>, it's nice to make contact with you.
How do I copy?
btu <CALL> de <MYCALL> kn
<RX>

 
/$ 5 2.3 CQ Answered
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<RXRSID:off>
*** <CALL> <CALL> *** de <MYCALL>
Thank you for answering my call
My name is <MYNAME>
How do I copy?
btu <CALL> de <MYCALL> kn
<RX>

 
/$ 6 3.1 Report 599
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<CLRTX>
<CLRRX>
Report 599

 
/$ 7 3.2 Report And Details
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<CALL> de <MYCALL>
Hello <NAME>, details as follows:
RST: <MYRST>
Name: <MYNAME>
QTH: <MYQTH>
Loc: <MYLOC>
btu <NAME> <CALL> de <MYCALL> kn
<RX>

 
/$ 8 3.3 Name & QTH
<MODEM:BPSK31>
I am <MYNAME> from Kiev/Ukraine
<MYCALL> / <MYNAME> <MYRST> <INFO1> kn
www.qrz.com/db/<MYCALL>

 
/$ 9 3.4 Exchange
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<CALL> EXCH
<RX>

 
/$ 10 3.5 Exchange Again
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<CALL> de <MYCALL> Exchange Exchange pse
<RX>

 
/$ 11 3.6 QSL
<MODEM:BPSK31>
<TX>
<CALL> QSL QSL de <MYCALL>
<RX>


